15 each primary election (, or in lieu thereof, a caucus or convention of a
16 political party), and an equal amount for each general election.
17 (2) For the office of member of the house of representatives, district
18 judge, district magistrate judge, district attorney or a candidate for local
19 office whose jurisdiction has a population that is fewer than 50,000, $500
