21 to a party committee, as defined in K.S.A. 25-4143(j)(1), (4), (5) or (6),
22 and amendments thereto, shall not exceed $50,000 in any calendar year.
23 (3) The aggregate amount contributed to any party committee, as
24 defined in K.S.A. 25-4143(j)(2), and amendments thereto, by a person
